lead_paragraph: Indians manager Terry Francona had his remarkable World Series record dented a bit with the Chicago Cubs' 3-2 win on Sunday, and he will have to wait at least two days for another crack at his third title.

headline.print_headline: Indians Manager Francona Tips Cap to Cubs
